1
00:00:07,069 --> 00:00:11,506
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,574 --> 00:00:15,101
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:15,177 --> 00:00:18,613
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,681 --> 00:00:22,276
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,351 --> 00:00:25,616
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,688 --> 00:00:27,622
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,425 --> 00:00:32,360
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,428 --> 00:00:36,228
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,632 --> 00:00:43,470
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,706 --> 00:00:50,771
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:57,212
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,353 --> 00:01:01,619
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,690 --> 00:01:05,285
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,361 --> 00:01:08,694
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,764 --> 00:01:12,393
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,468 --> 00:01:16,063
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:16,138 --> 00:01:19,630
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,708 --> 00:01:23,303
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,379 --> 00:01:27,475
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:31,831 --> 00:01:32,855
<i>Water Style!</i>

21
00:01:36,536 --> 00:01:38,003
- <i>Water Shark Bomb Jutsu!</i>
- <i>Water Shark Bomb Jutsu!</i>

22
00:01:42,943 --> 00:01:44,774
The same Jutsu as me?!

23
00:01:45,212 --> 00:01:48,010
Why have you shown up too?

24
00:01:48,448 --> 00:01:52,214
Well... I asked you to take care
of them earlier.

25
00:01:53,053 --> 00:01:55,385
But I kinda felt uneasy, you know.

26
00:01:59,793 --> 00:02:02,057
What business does
a Rogue Ninja like you

27
00:02:02,128 --> 00:02:04,562
have in this village now?

28
00:02:10,503 --> 00:02:12,061
Hatake Kakashi...

29
00:02:13,006 --> 00:02:18,842
<i>Sharingan vs. Sharingan</i>

30
00:02:34,928 --> 00:02:37,396
What?! Why?! Why?!

31
00:02:37,464 --> 00:02:41,924
Why do I have to go on a research trip
with you, Pervy Sage?

32
00:02:42,669 --> 00:02:46,730
Oh no, this isn't just any research trip.

33
00:02:47,073 --> 00:02:48,904
There's a woman whose data
I want to collect.

34
00:02:48,975 --> 00:02:50,442
So we have to look for her first.

35
00:02:50,677 --> 00:02:54,477
I really don't have time to accompany you
on your perverted research trip!

36
00:02:54,814 --> 00:02:56,509
Because I have training

37
00:02:57,250 --> 00:02:58,410
Hm? Training

38
00:02:58,551 --> 00:03:02,544
I will take lessons from Kakashi Sensei
and learn a variety of things, like Chidori!

39
00:03:04,291 --> 00:03:07,283
<i>Kakashi Sensei has been</i>
<i>playing favorites lately!</i>

40
00:03:07,994 --> 00:03:13,330
Well, I think that technique
is impossible for you to learn.

41
00:03:14,501 --> 00:03:18,665
More importantly...
That woman is really beautiful.

42
00:03:18,738 --> 00:03:20,103
You want to meet her, don't you?!

43
00:03:20,307 --> 00:03:21,433
Not at all.

44
00:03:21,841 --> 00:03:26,642
I'm not some kid who can
be cajoled by you, Pervy Sage!

45
00:03:26,913 --> 00:03:28,608
Anyway, no!

46
00:03:29,783 --> 00:03:31,876
Well, it can't be helped...

47
00:03:32,819 --> 00:03:37,017
Oh, well... I know Jutsu more amazing
than Chidori, but...

48
00:03:38,692 --> 00:03:41,786
It can't be helped...
Maybe I'll take Sasuke?

49
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,063
Of course I'll go!

50
00:03:45,598 --> 00:03:48,066
I'll pack my bags right away.

51
00:03:48,234 --> 00:03:51,260
Pervy Sage, don't move!

52
00:03:54,607 --> 00:03:58,043
I'll be darned... He's really a cute kid.

53
00:04:11,658 --> 00:04:14,024
<i>Those eyes are exactly the same</i>
<i>as they used to be in the past.</i>

54
00:04:14,427 --> 00:04:17,123
<i>That being said,</i>
<i>he is a true inheritor of the Sharingan...</i>

55
00:04:18,298 --> 00:04:21,165
<i>I have to assume the worst case scenario,</i>
<i>just in case.</i>

56
00:04:22,369 --> 00:04:26,066
This is a surprise...
No wonder you copied my Jutsu...

57
00:04:27,006 --> 00:04:31,204
So there really is a fellow
besides Itachi who has that eye.

58
00:04:31,911 --> 00:04:34,903
Your name is Kakashi,
the Copy Ninja, wasn't it?

59
00:04:35,815 --> 00:04:37,646
I'm the one who was surprised.

60
00:04:38,084 --> 00:04:41,485
I saw strange men in the tea house
and wondered who they were...

61
00:04:42,455 --> 00:04:44,787
There they were Itachi Uchiha and...

62
00:04:45,625 --> 00:04:49,117
the Mystery Man of Hidden Mist Village
Kisame Hoshigaki.

63
00:04:49,863 --> 00:04:54,197
Well, well... You know even my name.
It's an honor.

64
00:04:55,101 --> 00:04:59,094
I see. You're one of the
"Seven Ninja Swordsmen of the Mist."

65
00:04:59,672 --> 00:05:02,266
That huge sword is the "Shark Skin," right?

66
00:05:04,677 --> 00:05:08,636
I heard that kid Zabuza
had it out with you?

67
00:05:09,749 --> 00:05:10,613
Yeah...

68
00:05:16,189 --> 00:05:18,623
You are someone who's
well worth lopping off...

69
00:05:19,092 --> 00:05:20,650
Stop it... Kisame.

70
00:05:24,264 --> 00:05:28,496
If you were to go at it with that man,
it won't end without cost.

71
00:05:29,469 --> 00:05:33,735
And if you spend too much time,
another Shinobi would come running.

72
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:34,970
However...

73
00:05:35,475 --> 00:05:40,777
Don't lose sight of the goal...
You didn't come here to get injured!

74
00:05:41,214 --> 00:05:44,149
Let me hear that goal then?

75
00:05:54,027 --> 00:05:56,257
Just came to find something
we're looking for.

76
00:05:57,597 --> 00:05:58,894
Something you're looking for?

77
00:06:21,821 --> 00:06:24,085
The thing you're looking for...
What is it?

78
00:06:27,827 --> 00:06:31,024
I'm different from Kisame,
I won't take time.

79
00:06:34,868 --> 00:06:36,597
Ninja Art: Water Style.
Water wall!

80
00:06:45,411 --> 00:06:49,006
<i>That's some Jutsu speed.</i>
<i>My eyes couldn't follow the Sign.</i>

81
00:06:49,983 --> 00:06:51,974
<i>That Shuriken in the right hand</i>
<i>was a decoy...</i>

82
00:06:52,418 --> 00:06:54,886
<i>to use a Water Style Jutsu to launch</i>
<i>an attack below my foot...</i>

83
00:06:55,622 --> 00:06:57,522
That's what to expect from you, Kakashi.

84
00:06:57,790 --> 00:07:00,918
Your power of analytical eye... is great.

85
00:07:02,729 --> 00:07:05,493
A Shadow Clone?!
His Jutsu speed is too fast!

86
00:07:08,735 --> 00:07:09,929
<i>A water clone?!</i>

87
00:07:12,205 --> 00:07:16,039
<i>The Copy Ninja has done well this far</i>
<i>with Jutsu of my village.</i>

88
00:07:18,511 --> 00:07:19,944
Nice! Kakashi!

89
00:07:20,747 --> 00:07:21,475
Get down, Kurenai!

90
00:07:23,082 --> 00:07:24,447
This one is the Shadow Clone...

91
00:07:24,517 --> 00:07:25,040
Huh?

92
00:07:27,587 --> 00:07:29,020
Kakashi! Kurenai!

93
00:07:29,789 --> 00:07:32,019
<i>He made the Shadow Clone</i>
<i>body explode?!</i>

94
00:07:35,929 --> 00:07:37,988
A new Jutsu, a new Jutsu.

95
00:07:40,466 --> 00:07:42,957
Sakura's going to start to like me...

96
00:07:43,036 --> 00:07:43,798
Maybe!

97
00:07:45,071 --> 00:07:48,905
Kakashi Sensei and Sasuke
will be surprised!

98
00:07:58,785 --> 00:07:59,683
Kakashi...!

99
00:08:05,825 --> 00:08:06,951
Don't lower your guard...

100
00:08:07,393 --> 00:08:10,521
He's the guy who became a division chief
of Anbu Black Ops at 13 years old...

101
00:08:11,397 --> 00:08:12,955
To think he's this powerful...

102
00:08:13,499 --> 00:08:17,162
No, you haven't seen
this guy's strength yet.

103
00:08:20,406 --> 00:08:22,499
I didn't expect that you who are not
a member of the Uchiha clan

104
00:08:22,575 --> 00:08:25,203
would have mastered
the Sharingan to that extent...

105
00:08:25,812 --> 00:08:31,250
But your body isn't the Uchiha clan body
that goes with the eye.

106
00:08:32,151 --> 00:08:35,314
<i>That's right. As a result,</i>
<i>my stamina doesn't last...</i>

107
00:08:36,623 --> 00:08:41,424
There's a reason why the Uchiha Clan
was deemed the strongest and feared...

108
00:08:43,997 --> 00:08:48,934
I'll demonstrate the true strength
of Sharingan, the Kekkei Genkai!

109
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:52,162
<i>I-It can't be!</i>

110
00:08:52,905 --> 00:08:53,769
<i>This is bad!</i>

111
00:08:54,307 --> 00:08:56,241
Both of you! Don't look at his eyes!

112
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:02,048
Both of you! Don't look at his eyes!

113
00:09:06,753 --> 00:09:09,085
Both of you,
absolutely do <i>not</i> open your eyes...

114
00:09:09,656 --> 00:09:11,419
It's all over now if your eyes meet.

115
00:09:12,726 --> 00:09:16,321
Only people with Sharingan
can have a go with that technique.

116
00:09:16,763 --> 00:09:18,890
Indeed with Sharingan,

117
00:09:19,266 --> 00:09:22,497
you can resist this Mangekyo Sharingan
to a certain extent.

118
00:09:23,637 --> 00:09:24,569
However...

119
00:09:26,573 --> 00:09:29,064
this special Visual Jutsu of Sharingan,

120
00:09:29,243 --> 00:09:32,007
Genjutsu: Tsukuyomi, Nightmare Realm,
is unbreakable.

121
00:09:33,046 --> 00:09:35,241
The only person who can bring me down
is someone

122
00:09:35,315 --> 00:09:38,079
using the same Kekkei Genkai,
a Sharingan user...

123
00:09:44,858 --> 00:09:46,018
<i>Sasuke...</i>

124
00:10:03,644 --> 00:10:07,740
I wonder how much you can take
without the Kekkei Genkai?

125
00:10:24,498 --> 00:10:26,796
The one just now was... Genjutsu?

126
00:10:27,434 --> 00:10:29,061
In the world of Tsukuyomi...

127
00:10:31,204 --> 00:10:32,933
Both space and time...

128
00:10:35,909 --> 00:10:38,639
and mass...
I control them all.

129
00:10:41,148 --> 00:10:43,275
For the next 72 hours...

130
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:46,050
I'll stab you continually with swords.

131
00:11:04,204 --> 00:11:05,262
That's...

132
00:11:06,373 --> 00:11:08,000
In the world of Tsukuyomi...

133
00:11:09,276 --> 00:11:11,403
Both space and time...

134
00:11:13,814 --> 00:11:17,181
and mass...
I control them all.

135
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:23,285
<i>Calm down... This is Genjutsu.</i>

136
00:11:24,658 --> 00:11:28,094
It's best not to be optimistic
and think it's an illusion.

137
00:11:33,867 --> 00:11:36,267
This pain is not an illusion.

138
00:11:39,272 --> 00:11:42,901
This pain is absolutely
no different from reality.

139
00:11:50,517 --> 00:11:54,078
How long will your spirit sustain?

140
00:12:29,222 --> 00:12:34,785
There's...
71 hours 59 minutes 59 seconds left.

141
00:12:36,430 --> 00:12:37,124
<i>Wha...?!</i>

142
00:12:37,564 --> 00:12:39,759
<i>S-Since then...?!</i>

143
00:12:44,137 --> 00:12:46,469
<i>That's all the time that has passed?!</i>

144
00:13:41,161 --> 00:13:42,389
What happened, Kakashi?!

145
00:13:42,462 --> 00:13:44,191
Are you saying we should keep
our eyes closed still?!

146
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,662
N-Not... yet...

147
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,734
What happened?!

148
00:13:51,304 --> 00:13:54,364
Just as that guy finished speaking,
you suddenly fell over!

149
00:13:57,344 --> 00:14:02,475
Three days in that world is less than
a moment in the actual world, huh...

150
00:14:03,850 --> 00:14:06,478
But... why doesn't he kill me?

151
00:14:07,487 --> 00:14:09,648
He could easily do so, if he wants to...

152
00:14:10,557 --> 00:14:15,119
Whoa... To take that Jutsu without causing
his spirit to collapse.

153
00:14:16,029 --> 00:14:17,053
But Itachi...

154
00:14:17,364 --> 00:14:21,095
it's also dangerous for you
to overuse those eyes.

155
00:14:25,338 --> 00:14:27,101
The thing you're looking for...

156
00:14:27,974 --> 00:14:29,202
is it Sasuke?

157
00:14:32,179 --> 00:14:36,138
No... the legacy of the Fourth Hokage...

158
00:14:38,385 --> 00:14:40,182
These guys.
What the heck are they planning...?

159
00:14:50,163 --> 00:14:51,528
<i>So, Naruto, is it...?</i>

160
00:14:52,199 --> 00:14:53,666
It's been a long time...

161
00:14:55,435 --> 00:14:58,131
How many years has it been
since you returned to the village?

162
00:15:04,177 --> 00:15:05,166
Kakashi...

163
00:15:08,882 --> 00:15:10,873
I will keep Naruto under my care.

164
00:15:12,652 --> 00:15:14,813
It was an understandable decision
of the Third Hokage

165
00:15:14,888 --> 00:15:18,449
who appointed you to
the role of watching over Naruto...

166
00:15:19,059 --> 00:15:23,462
But even at your level,
you may not be able to handle it properly.

167
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,895
What in the world are you saying?

168
00:15:28,568 --> 00:15:33,767
I've been observing Orochimaru
ever since he left the village...

169
00:15:34,774 --> 00:15:39,507
It was obvious that he would return
to this village sooner or later.

170
00:15:40,547 --> 00:15:44,540
All told, at first I was concerned
only about him, but...

171
00:15:46,553 --> 00:15:47,485
What is it?

172
00:15:48,488 --> 00:15:51,013
The guy joined an organization.

173
00:15:52,425 --> 00:15:53,255
An organization?

174
00:15:55,495 --> 00:15:57,053
What are the details of the organization?

175
00:15:58,898 --> 00:16:00,957
I don't know much of the details,

176
00:16:01,134 --> 00:16:05,366
but it's a small organization known
as Akatsuki made up of nine Shinobi.

177
00:16:06,573 --> 00:16:09,667
Until recently, they weren't making
any dramatic moves

178
00:16:09,743 --> 00:16:11,870
except some cloak and dagger activities.

179
00:16:11,945 --> 00:16:14,038
The biggest concern is
the members of that organization.

180
00:16:15,215 --> 00:16:18,343
Almost all of them are listed
on the Bingo Book,

181
00:16:18,518 --> 00:16:22,352
all S rank deviant criminals.

182
00:16:23,723 --> 00:16:27,250
That Itachi is among them.

183
00:16:28,828 --> 00:16:32,628
If the nine of them get together,
their intent will not be volunteer activities.

184
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:37,133
Since you've been told this much,
you already know what it means.

185
00:16:42,676 --> 00:16:46,635
But recently, Orochimaru pulled out
of the organization.

186
00:16:47,047 --> 00:16:48,776
And at that time,

187
00:16:48,848 --> 00:16:52,045
other members of the organization
went in to action in different areas,

188
00:16:52,118 --> 00:16:54,279
in pairs gathering Jutsu and things.

189
00:16:55,588 --> 00:16:58,682
Is there proof that one of those
things is the Nine Tailed Fox?

190
00:16:59,426 --> 00:17:02,088
It's possible.

191
00:17:02,896 --> 00:17:06,957
Because it's one of the spirits
who possess the strongest Chakra...

192
00:17:09,569 --> 00:17:10,536
Kakashi...

193
00:17:10,770 --> 00:17:16,106
Sooner or later, that Naruto will have
to live watching his back...

194
00:17:18,311 --> 00:17:19,938
That's his destiny.

195
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:26,480
For now, you should keep
your eyes on Sasuke.

196
00:17:27,454 --> 00:17:30,423
It's necessary for you to teach him
how to use his Sharingan.

197
00:17:31,558 --> 00:17:35,221
I'll take care of Naruto for a while.

198
00:17:42,001 --> 00:17:46,529
The Nine Tailed Fox inside Naruto
is your target?

199
00:17:49,509 --> 00:17:53,843
I know that you two aren't
the only ones on the move...

200
00:17:55,682 --> 00:17:59,516
The name of your organization is
Akatsuki, right?

201
00:18:02,555 --> 00:18:03,579
Akatsuki?

202
00:18:04,324 --> 00:18:09,193
Kisame! We'll take Kakashi.
Erase the other two.

203
00:18:13,066 --> 00:18:15,626
Severe Leaf Hurricanes!

204
00:18:26,279 --> 00:18:27,371
Who are you?

205
00:18:28,982 --> 00:18:32,042
The Leaf's noble, blue fierce animal...

206
00:18:32,952 --> 00:18:34,180
Mighty Guy!

207
00:18:35,155 --> 00:18:38,818
What a sight...
Shouldn't you be called a strange beast?

208
00:18:39,526 --> 00:18:41,118
Don't underestimate that man...

209
00:18:41,895 --> 00:18:44,159
<i>That man is Itachi!</i>

210
00:18:53,506 --> 00:18:55,064
You did this to Kakashi...?

211
00:18:55,675 --> 00:18:59,611
Don't look at Itachi's eyes, Guy!
You'll be caught up in his Jutsu!

212
00:19:00,013 --> 00:19:02,038
I know that already!

213
00:19:02,715 --> 00:19:07,448
In order to fight Kakashi,
I devised ways to battle the Sharingan.

214
00:19:10,089 --> 00:19:11,954
Open your eyes, both of you!

215
00:19:12,091 --> 00:19:13,615
B-But...

216
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:16,351
When you battle with the Sharingan,

217
00:19:16,429 --> 00:19:18,522
it's not a problem if
you don't look at those eyes!

218
00:19:19,265 --> 00:19:21,495
You work around it by
gaining insight into his movements

219
00:19:21,568 --> 00:19:23,536
by looking constantly at his feet.

220
00:19:25,038 --> 00:19:28,030
Now that you mention it,
you're probably right, but...

221
00:19:28,808 --> 00:19:31,777
You're the only one who can do that.

222
00:19:32,111 --> 00:19:32,941
That's true...

223
00:19:33,813 --> 00:19:35,280
There's a knack to reading

224
00:19:35,348 --> 00:19:37,509
all of your opponents movements
only by his feet.

225
00:19:38,017 --> 00:19:40,315
But I can't teach it to you
in this emergency.

226
00:19:40,653 --> 00:19:42,587
Just get used to it right now!

227
00:19:44,257 --> 00:19:44,985
What should we do?

228
00:19:45,358 --> 00:19:47,622
Kurenai, get Kakashi to the medical team.

229
00:19:48,962 --> 00:19:50,691
Asuma, you are my back up!

230
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:51,558
Okay!

231
00:19:53,366 --> 00:19:57,393
And until the reinforcements of
Anbu Black Ops I arranged for arrive,

232
00:19:58,071 --> 00:20:00,767
I will hang out with you guys.

233
00:20:00,940 --> 00:20:03,966
Interesting...
That's some nerve...

234
00:20:05,278 --> 00:20:07,303
Kisame... Pull the plug.

235
00:20:08,414 --> 00:20:10,644
We didn't come to have a war.

236
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:13,744
It's too bad,
but no more of this nonsense.

237
00:20:14,454 --> 00:20:15,318
We're leaving.

238
00:20:16,923 --> 00:20:19,756
Too bad... I was finally feeling motivated.

239
00:20:20,527 --> 00:20:22,392
It can't be helped.

240
00:20:35,275 --> 00:20:36,367
All right!

241
00:20:46,185 --> 00:20:48,085
Here I go!

242
00:20:49,889 --> 00:20:51,914
Y-You're putting too much spirit into it.

243
00:20:52,458 --> 00:20:57,157
You're not training on a mountain retreat,
you know that, right?

244
00:21:09,543 --> 00:21:13,479
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

245
00:21:14,481 --> 00:21:18,440
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

246
00:21:19,753 --> 00:21:27,717
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

247
00:21:28,695 --> 00:21:30,788
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

248
00:21:33,567 --> 00:21:36,593
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

249
00:21:37,037 --> 00:21:41,974
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

250
00:21:42,108 --> 00:21:47,569
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

251
00:21:47,847 --> 00:21:52,750
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

252
00:21:52,819 --> 00:21:57,722
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

253
00:21:57,791 --> 00:22:06,961
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

254
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:12,303
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

255
00:22:12,372 --> 00:22:18,208
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

256
00:22:19,846 --> 00:22:29,983
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

257
00:22:38,965 --> 00:22:41,490
There's a super beautiful
young lady over there!

258
00:22:41,568 --> 00:22:42,796
She just winked at us!

259
00:22:42,869 --> 00:22:45,997
Look, Naruto!
She must be interested in us!

260
00:22:46,206 --> 00:22:47,639
She may be cuter than Sakura!

261
00:22:47,707 --> 00:22:49,504
- All right, Naruto!
- Yeah!

262
00:22:49,709 --> 00:22:52,075
Go back, train,
then go to bed.

263
00:22:52,145 --> 00:22:54,375
You always do that to me!

264
00:22:54,848 --> 00:22:59,649
Next time: "Jiraiya:
Naruto's Potential Disaster!"

265
00:23:00,220 --> 00:23:02,450
What are we gonna do
about my training?!
